  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"314\" data-backw=\"578\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"314\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100011872\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e5bdcd8-38f5-4027-e69c-e15a8581b300/public\" style=\"width: 578px; pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e5bdcd8-38f5-4027-e69c-e15a8581b300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"139\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100011873\" data-ratio=\"0.23981481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c41094e9-8798-4147-8dc0-8887ecff4500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c41094e9-8798-4147-8dc0-8887ecff4500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <article data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{},[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqiiyf3zsy6qbm1m6&quot;,&quot;jc&quot;:&quot;justify&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;QwQ-32B 在一系列基准测试中&quot;],[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;进行了评估，测试了数学推理、编程能力和通用能力。下图展示了 QwQ-32B 与领先其他模型的性能对比，包括 DeepSeek-R1-Distilled-Qwen-32B、DeepSeek-R1-Distilled-Llama-70B、o1-mini 以及原始的 DeepSeek-R1。&quot;]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"3M0Oz581PBGLqzeE\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">QwQ-32B 在一系列基准测试中进行了评估，测试了</span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Ya