, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);color: rgb(97, 92, 237);\">通用能力</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">。下图展示了 QwQ-32B 与其他模型的性能对比，包括 DeepSeek-R1-Distilled-Qwen-32B、DeepSeek-R1-Distilled-Llama-70B、o1-mini 以及原始的 DeepSeek-R1。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"></span></p>\n   <article data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{},[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wq78r29hod77xmvxf&quot;,&quot;jc&quot;:&quot;justify&quot;},[&quot;img&quot;,{&quot;effectExtent&quot;:{&quot;bottom&quot;:0,&quot;left&quot;:0,&quot;right&quot;:0,&quot;top&quot;:0},&quot;height&quot;:421.91875,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;qwq-32b-final.jpeg&quot;,&quot;realName&quot;:&quot;image1.jpg&quot;,&quot;rotation&quot;:0,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://alidocs.dingtalk.com/core/api/resources/img/5eecdaf48460cde5383a224bd75cadf189c59fa748a121cc58e70b814913bc360a414d3de9277d871abf3af1cbd7524982c26dfcb595b1f11fcbdcc8df8e5225a1443b417bf7447e4014e7c253e469e6f37f9902b76e5af3fc653b69905bac42?tmpCode=0f186491-ee7a-4912-ad9d-df4f02b4f2ec&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:748,&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqjc37un6w4hntcxo&quot;,&quot;extraData&quot;:{&quot;resourceId&quot;:&quot;09e0224e-914d-4479-9921-4105dce9b87c&quot;,&quot;metaData&quot;:{&quot;size&quot;:320088,&quot;originWidth&quot;:3035,&quot;originHeight&quot;:1713,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;jpg&quot;,&quot;ratio&quot;:1}}},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;&quot;]]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"3M0Oz581PBGLqzeE\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"326\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100011875\" data-ratio=\"0.5648148148148148\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c621a82-051f-4b15-b3d8-d0d780b60a00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1c621a82-051f-4b15-b3d8-d0d780b60a00/public\"></p>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p>\n    <article data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{},[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqjhvatbk9buuj6g&quot;,&quot;jc&quot;:&quot;justify&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;在数学能力的 AIME24 测评集上，以及评估代码能力的 LiveCodeBench 中，千问 QwQ-32B 测试表现与 DeepSeek-R1 相当，远胜于 o1-mini 及相同尺寸的 R1 后续模型。&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqg7fzihpdvxu2nmp&quot;,&quot;jc&quot;:&quot;justify&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqg7m3kn63qrzmltq&quot;,&quot;jc&quot;:&quot;justify&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;由 Meta 首席科学家杨立昆领衔的“最难 LLMs 体育排行榜” LiveBench、谷歌等提出的指令遵循能力IFEval体育集、由加州大学伯克利分校等提出的评估调用函数或工具方面的BFCL测试中，千问QwQ-32B的得分均超越了DeepSeek- R1。&quot;]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"3M0Oz581PBGLqzeE\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">在数学能力的 AIME24 测评集上，以及评估代码能力的 LiveCodeBench 中，通义千问&nbsp;QwQ-32B 测试表现与 DeepSeek-R1 相当，远胜于 o1-mini 及相同尺寸的 R1 后续模型。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p>\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">由 Meta 首席科学家杨立昆领衔的“最难 LLMs 测评榜” LiveBench、谷歌等提出的指令遵循能力 IFEval 测试集、由加州大学伯克利分校等提出的评估调用函数或工具方面的 BFCL 测试中，QwQ-32B 的得分均超越了 DeepSeek- R1。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><br></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"126\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100011879\" data-ratio=\"0.21851851851851853\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/59f69422-e035-421d-accc-6ae3229dcd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/59f69422-e035-421d-accc-6ae3229dcd00/public\"></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p>\n     <article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"3M0Oz581PBGLqzeE\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">在冷启动基础上，我们针对数学和编程任务、通用能力分别进行了两轮大规模强化学习。在初始阶段，我们特别</span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);color: rgb(97, 92, 237);\">针对数学和编程任务进行了强化学习。</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">与依赖传统的奖励模型（奖励模型）不同，我们通过生成答案的正确性来为数学问题提供反馈，并通过代码执行服务器评估生成的代码成功，通过测试来提供代码是否提供反馈。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">我们发现在强化学习扩展过程中，随着训练轮次的推进，这两个领域中的性能均表现出持续的提升。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">在第一阶段的强化学习之后，我们增加了另一个</span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);color: rgb(97, 92, 237);\">针对通用能力的强化学习。</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">该阶段使用通用奖励模型和基于一些规则的验证器进行训练。我们发现，通过少量步骤的通用强化学习，可以提升其他通用能力，同时在数学和编程任务上的性能没有显着下降。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">此外，通义千问 QwQ-32B 模型还集成了与智能体 Agent 相关的能力，使其能够在使用工具的同时进行批判性思考，并根据环境反馈调整推理过程。</span></p>\n     </article>\n     <p><br></p>\n     <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100011877\" data-ratio=\"0.21666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da4763e4-7924-4e1f-3a35-93fa1d914500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/da4763e4-7924-4e1f-3a35-93fa1d914500/public\"></p>\n     <p><br></p>\n     <article data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{},[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqvvypzvhmhi5kk2&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;目前，通义 QwQ-32B 已经在魔搭社区 HuggingFace 及 GitHub 等平台开源，并采用了 Apache 2.0 开源协议，欢迎大家下载体验。&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqzgbfanlfub5hyjf&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;&quot;]]],[&quot;p&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m7wqzgghu6obdfkui1k&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;spacing&quot;:0.20400000000000001,&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;bold&quot;:false,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;大家也可以通过百炼平台直接调用模型 API 服务，&quot;],[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;sz&quot;:12,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;rgb(64, 64, 64)&quot;,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;以下为调用示例代码：&quot;]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"3M0Oz581PBGLqzeE\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">目前，通义千问 QwQ-32B 已经在魔搭社区及 HuggingFace 开源，并采用了 Apache 2.0 开源协议，欢迎大家下载体验。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\">以下为 API 调用示例代码：</span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.2px;caret-color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><br></span></p>\n      <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n       <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n        <li></li>\n       </ul>\n       <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"python\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">from</span> openai <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">import</span> OpenAI</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">import</span> os</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># Initialize OpenAI client</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">client = OpenAI(</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># If the environment variable is not configured, replace with your API Key: api_key=\"sk-xxx\"</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># How to get an API Key：https://help.aliyun.com/zh/model-studio/developer-reference/get-api-key</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    api_key=os.getenv(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"DASHSCOPE_API_KEY\"</span>),</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    base_url=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1\"</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">reasoning_content = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"\"</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">content = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"\"</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">is_answering = <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">False</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">completion = client.chat.completions.create(</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    model=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"qwq-32b\"</span>,</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    messages=[</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        {<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"role\"</span>: <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"user\"</span>, <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"content\"</span>: <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Which is larger, 9.9 or 9.11?\"</span>}</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    ],</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    stream=<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">True</span>,</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># Uncomment the following line to return token usage in the last chunk</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># stream_options={</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">#     \"include_usage\": True</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># }</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">print(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"\\n\"</span> + <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"=\"</span> * <span class=\"code-snippet__number\">20</span> + <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"reasoning content\"</span> + <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"=\"</span> * <span class=\"code-snippet__number\">20</span> + <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"\\n\"</span>)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">for</span> chunk <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">in</span> completion:</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># If chunk.choices is empty, print usage</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">not</span> chunk.choices:</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        print(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"\\nUsage:\"</span>)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        print(chunk.usage)</span></code><code><span c